According to Silulumanzi Technical Services teams are on the ground resolving this problem in order to fix the pump which is estimated to take up to two weeks. We kindly urge the community to use water wisely for the next two weeks as all of Nsikazi will be effected from KaNyamazane to KaBokweni. READ: KaNyamazane experiences bulk water supply interruption due to strike Silulumanzi is kindly requesting the community to report water leaks and interruptions to 086 174 5858 or at 086 174 5858 after hours.